This was the best I could find on Amazon but nowhere near as practical or good looking as my previous dish drainer. I needed one to fit over my sink and also sit on the counter next to the sink. The drainer is made of extremely sharp metal making it dangerous to move even if you’re super careful. I checked the measurements to make sure it would extend enough to fit across my sink but it’s wider than I thought, so it’s not practical to wash other items alongside. And if you move it, the plastic covers that keep it from damaging the counter fall off easily and are likely to get lost.
